Description: automatically fix lintian problems
 This package contains a set of scripts that can automatically fix more than 160
 common lintian issues in Debian packages.
 .
 It comes with a wrapper script that invokes the scripts, updates
 the changelog (if desired) and commits each change to
 version control.
 .
 The following other codemods are included:
 .
  * apply-multiarch-hints: applies multiarch hints to debian/control
  * deb-scrub-obsolete: removes obsolete dependencies and maintscript snippets
  * deb-vcs-publish: adds VCS metadata to debian/control
  * fix-watch-file: updates the debian/watch file to use the latest format
